    "description": "A synced web radio player for everyone in a space. Any space member can pick a station from a large list of public web stations — rock, pop, ambient, jazz, French, Italian, Australian, NPR, chiptune, and more — and everyone else in the space hears the same audio simultaneously. Play/pause and station selection are shared; each viewer's volume and mute are local and remembered between sessions.",
